Cliff Richard, 81, has arrived at Wimbledon Day Five wearing an eye-catching white blazer paired with a matching tie. Â Cliff styled the garment over a black shirt, black trousers, patent leather shoes and a studded belt.As he has done all week, Cliff pinned a red rose on his left lapel to finish the look.The iconic singer beamed as he arrived at the All England Lawn Tennis and Croquet Club on Friday.He is clearly looking forward to the day ahead which will include Djokovic, Jabeur, Watson and Norrie in action.